2004-08-08  MenTaLguY  <mental@rydia.net>

	* src/sp-flowregion.cpp, src/sp-flowtext.cpp, src/sp-offset.cpp,
	  src/splivarot.cpp, src/display/nr-arena-shape.cpp,
