	  collection

2004-06-06  Bryce Harrington <bryce@bryceharrington.org>

	* libnrtype/nr-type-xft.cpp, libnrtype/nr-font.cpp,
	  libnrtype/nr-rasterfont.cpp, libnrtype/nr-type-directory.cpp,
